##
## Introduction
##
@node introduction "Introduction"

 Blanker is an attempt to provide the Amiga community with a future-compatible,
 easily expandable screen blanker.

 I would like to provide a platform for others to write custom screen blanker
 modules when the whim strikes and not have to worry about the difficulties
 associated with setting up a Commodities interface and dealing with
 concurrency problems.

 Additionally, there currently exist no AGA compatible screen blankers. So, in
 the long-lasting tradition of necessity being the mother of invention, I
 created Blanker.
@endnode

